                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>While Burrowing, the sapper squad can position its segments into a 20-foot-wide straight line and move at half Speed to leave a 20-foot-wide tunnel behind them that can be safely traversed by other creatures. Unless shored up by a crew of skilled laborers, the tunnel collapses after 10 minutes.</p>"
