            "img": "systems/pf2e/icons/actions/TwoActions.webp",
            "name": "Fire in the Hole!",
            "sort": 500000,
            "system": {
                "actionType": {
                    "value": "action"
                },
                "actions": {
                    "value": 2
                },
                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>The squad bombards a @Template[type:burst|distance:10] within 30 feet with satchel charges, dealing @Damage[2d6[fire],1d6[bludgeoning]|options:area-damage]{2d6 fire damage and 1d6 bludgeoning damage} to all creatures in the area (@Check[reflex|dc:18|basic] save). On a critical failure, a creature is also @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Deafened] for 1 round. When the squad is reduced to 2 segments, this area decreases to a @Template[type:burst|distance:5].</p>"
                },
