                    "value": 1
                },
                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p><span class=\"action-glyph\">1</span> to <span class=\"action-glyph\">3</span></p>\n<p><strong>Frequency</strong> once per round</p><hr /><p><strong>Effect</strong> The sapper squad strikes with their picks against enemies in a @Template[type:emanation|distance:5] with a @Check[reflex|dc:18|basic] save. The damage depends on the number of actions.</p>\n<p><span class=\"action-glyph\">1</span> @Damage[1d6[piercing]|options:area-damage] damage</p>\n<p><span class=\"action-glyph\">2</span> @Damage[(2d6+4)[piercing]|options:area-damage] damage</p>\n<p><span class=\"action-glyph\">3</span> @Damage[(2d6+7)[piercing]|options:area-damage] damage</p>"
